import React from 'react'
import { Header, Icon, Image, Menu, Segment, Sidebar } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const SidebarExampleVisible = () => (
  <Sidebar.Pushable as={Segment}>
    <Sidebar
      as={Menu}
      animation='overlay'
      icon='labeled'
      direction='right'
      inverted
      vertical
      visible
      width='thin'
    >
      <Menu.Item as='a'>
        <Icon name='home' />
        Home
      </Menu.Item>
      <Menu.Item as='a'>
        <Icon name='gamepad' />
        Games
      </Menu.Item>
      <Menu.Item as='a'>
        <Icon name='camera' />
        Channels
      </Menu.Item>
    </Sidebar>

  </Sidebar.Pushable>
)

export default SidebarExampleVisible
